Package: sportTheoryAI
Title: Extract Theoretical Frameworks from Sports Science Research Using Local LLMs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Author", "Name", email = "author@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A reproducible pipeline for extracting explicit and implicit theoretical
    frameworks from applied sports science research article introductions using locally
    hosted large language models via Ollama. Produces structured JSON outputs suitable
    for systematic review, meta-analysis, and academic validation.
